1. *Pogrešila* sam što sam ti verovala. (I made a mistake by trusting you.)
2. Ona je *pogrešila* u proceni situacije. (She made a mistake in assessing the situation.)
3. *Pogrešila* bih ako ne bih pokušala. (I would be making a mistake if I didn't try.)
4. *Pogrešila* sam u prepisivanju zadatka. (I made a mistake by copying the assignment.)
5. Kada sam te nazvala, mislila sam da sam *pogrešila* broj. (When I called you, I thought I had dialed the wrong number.)
6. Oni su *pogrešili* put i sada su izgubljeni. (They took the wrong road and are now lost.)
7. Njena odluka se pokazala kao *pogrešna*. (Her decision proved to be wrong.)
8. Molim vas da mi oprostite što sam *pogrešio*. (Please forgive me for my mistake.)